OL,3,C'Reasonable force' will be used to
OL,4,Cmake offenders attend court for
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FThe Justice Secretary has backed the
OL,8,Fmove to pass 'Olivia's Law' - giving
OL,9,Fjudges the power to order "reasonable
OL,10,Fforce" to make offenders attend
OL,11,Fsentencing.
OL,13,FIt comes after the prime minister met
OL,14,Fwith Cheryl Korbel, the mother of
OL,15,Fmurdered nine-year-old Olivia Pratt-
OL,16,FKorbel, on 21 January, after she began
OL,17,Fa campaign when Thomas Cashman, the
OL,18,Fgunman who killed Olivia did not
OL,19,Fappear in court to hear his life
OL,20,Fsentence in April 2023.
