OL,3,C'Reasonable force' will be used to
OL,4,Cmake offenders attend court for
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FKeir Starmer said he would give judges
OL,8,Fpowers to force criminals to appear in
OL,9,Fthe dock when they are being sentenced.
OL,11,FThe law change is expected to be made
OL,12,Fin the Victims, Courts and Public
OL,13,FProtection Bill, which will be laid in
OL,14,FParliament in the next few months.
OL,16,FThe legislation will aim to
OL,17,F"strengthen community policing, give
OL,18,Fthe police greater powers to deal with
OL,19,Fanti-social behaviour and strengthen
OL,20,Fsupport for victims", according to the
OL,21,FKing's Speech.
