OL,3,C'Reasonable force' will be used to
OL,4,Cmake offenders attend court for
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FDuring Justice questions in the
OL,8,FCommons, Justice Secretary Shabana
OL,9,FMahmood said criminals "add insult to
OL,10,Finjury" by failing to attend
OL,11,Fsentencing hearings.
OL,13,FShe said she had met Olivia's mother,
OL,14,Falong with the prime minister.
OL,16,FShe told MPs: "I will be legislating
OL,17,Fto give judges the power to order
OL,18,Fattendance at sentencing hearings, and
OL,19,FI will make it clear in the law that
OL,20,Freasonable force can be used to make
OL,21,Fsure that this happens.
