OL,7,F"The Prime Minister and I met with
OL,8,FCheryl Korbel last week to discuss
OL,9,Fthese proposals, and we will ensure
OL,10,Fthat the families of other victims are
OL,11,Finvolved before the Bill is put before
OL,12,Fthe House."
OL,14,FCheryl's MP, Labour's Anneliese
OL,15,FMidgley for Knowsley said: "Cheryl is
OL,16,Fpleased that the Government is
OL,17,Fcommitted to implementing Olivia's law
OL,18,Fwithout delay.
