OL,7,F"Can the minister ensure that Cheryl
OL,8,Fis involved in the development of this
OL,9,Flaw, placing victims and their
OL,10,Ffamilies at the heart of the justice
OL,11,Fsystem?"
OL,13,FMs Mahmood replied: "We have committed
OL,14,Fto introducing that legislation before
OL,15,Fthis summer, and I will, of course, as
OL,16,Fpromised last week, consult with
OL,17,FOlivia's family as well as the
OL,18,Ffamilies of other victims where
OL,19,Fattendance at sentencing hearings has
OL,20,Fcaused problems."
