OL,3,C'Reasonable force' will be used to
OL,4,Cmake offenders attend court for
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FFollowing the meeting, a Number 10
OL,8,Fspokesman said killers who refuse to
OL,9,Fface grieving families in court are
OL,10,F"beyond cowardly", but if defendants
OL,11,Fare "purposefully disruptive" or
OL,12,F"offensive" during proceedings then
OL,13,Ftheir attendance may not be
OL,14,Fappropriate.
OL,16,FDowning Street was asked whether the
OL,17,Fplans may need to be rethought to
OL,18,Faccount for defendants such as
OL,19,FSouthport killer Axel Rudakubana, who
OL,20,Frepeatedly shouted and interrupted
OL,21,Fproceedings at his sentencing.
